text: Camilla Cattaneo (born 12 February 1990) is an Italian synchronised swimmer. She competed in the team event at the 2016 Summer Olympics. Cattaneo is an athlete of the Gruppo Sportivo Fiamme Oro. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Italian synchronized swimmers Category:Olympic synchronized swimmers of Italy Category:Synchronized swimmers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Artistic swimmers of Fiamme Oro
